TASK_DESCRIPTION=Freelancers must always find or create a task before starting work. On startup: check doey task list for unassigned tasks, claim one or create a new one. Then rename their own pane via tmux select-pane -T to reflect the task they are working on (e.g. 'worker-task-5'). No freelancer should ever be idle without a task. This is a behavioral change to the freelancer agent definition.
